This skill embeds Chocolate Doom compiled to WebAssembly
(cloudflare/doom-wasm lineage) and the freely redistributable
DOOM shareware WAD (DOOM1.WAD).

Chocolate Doom is licensed under the GNU GPL v2 (see COPYING).
DOOM1.WAD is shareware data from id Software and may be freely
redistributed.

Engine glue JS/WASM vendored from the @nicejsisverycool/tizendoom
npm package (based on cloudflare/doom-wasm).
